description:
Danny starts the show off talking about the upcoming Sex and the City reboot, then dive's into this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured nude pics and the promise of Biden. After that, Danny welcomes Tamra Judge, formerly of The Real Housewives of Orange County to talk about her time on the show, a potential return, what she thinks of the women, and more!


RHOA: 6:30ish

Tamra Interview: 14:20ish
